  <name>Asteroids Revenge</name>
  <summary>Evade lasers as an enigmatic entity</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Asteroids Revenge is an exciting arcade-style game where you must navigate through an asteroid field while battling against a crooked spaceship. Dodge its lasers and fight back to emerge victorious!</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Fast-paced gameplay</li>
      <li>Challenging lasers</li>
      <li>minimal graphics</li>
      <li>Engaging sound effects</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
